data.description: Assumable loan, buyers must meet all qualifications.  3 story home has 5 bedrooms , 3 1/2 baths. excellence in design and architecture. Laminate flooring throughout the 1st floor. Flex / office room as you enter the home.  Granite counters, tile back splash and stainless appliances along with a huge  island.  and huge island.  Second floor has large loft area, master bedroom with a luxurious 5ft shower with tile surround. 3 additional bedrooms with separate bath with dual vanity.  On the third floor is a large loft that can be used additional bedroom / office /media room that has its own full bathroom.  Large  2 car garage with huge fenced back yard with koi pond
